"soon" should be... now.

27:16.358 --> 27:18.947
And then, he said that if I
couldn't get you to come out,

27:19.085 --> 27:21.950
he'd make me pay for it.

27:22.088 --> 27:22.951
Personally.
Oh, my God.

27:23.089 --> 27:25.505
Alright.
I'm coming. Just...

27:25.644 --> 27:28.163
page me if anything changes, immediately.

27:34.687 --> 27:37.276
Uh, mind if I stay
with Connor?

27:39.140 --> 27:42.764
I-I heard Tia tell Dr. Wilson
they were gonna name him Connor.

27:44.524 --> 27:45.629
Hi, Connor.

27:58.228 --> 27:59.470
What do you need,
Yasuda?

27:59.608 --> 28:01.093
Sorry I disappeared.

28:01.231 --> 28:03.405
Did I miss anything?

28:03.543 --> 28:05.097
Right.

28:05.235 --> 28:06.926
Could I sit with her
