28:07.064 --> 28:09.342
Let you take a break,
grab some coffee?

28:09.480 --> 28:12.000
No.
Oh, um...

28:12.138 --> 28:13.243
Okay.
Then I'm-- I'm--

28:13.381 --> 28:16.108
No, she's hypotensive
and slightly tachy.

28:16.246 --> 28:18.420
She's still bleeding
from her abdomen.

28:20.008 --> 28:21.596
Oh, look at
the wound vac.

28:21.734 --> 28:22.873
Okay, uh, call the O.R.

28:23.011 --> 28:24.806
Get the team up here.
Get over here.

28:24.944 --> 28:26.428
S-Shouldn't we be taking her
back to the O.R.?

28:26.566 --> 28:27.429
No time.

28:29.086 --> 28:30.639
Y-Yasuda.

28:30.778 --> 28:32.814
If I'm going to open this woman
up, I need your hands.

28:32.952 --> 28:35.437
- We're opening her up here?
- We need to move,
right now!

28:38.786 --> 28:41.650
You'll have to wear the sling
for about four weeks,

28:41.789 --> 28:43.445
but keep your elbow, wrist,
and hand moving.

28:43.583 --> 28:45.068
It'll help.

28:45.206 --> 28:47.139
And don't ignore
the PT exercises

28:47.277 --> 28:48.727
no matter
how exhausted you get.

28:52.489 --> 28:53.973
Honestly, it...

28:54.111 --> 28:55.837
it wouldn't be
a terrible idea

28:55.975 --> 28:58.081
to take a break from the road
for a couple of weeks.

29:02.464 --> 29:04.535
Thank you.

29:08.022 --> 29:10.162
It's me.

29:12.958 --> 29:15.098
Talk to me.

29:15.236 --> 29:17.686
You know, the irony...

29:17.825 --> 29:20.828
of all of this
is that these people

29:20.966 --> 29:23.416
are targeting me
for the abortion care

29:23.554 --> 29:24.935
that I provide

29:25.073 --> 29:29.008
when that is actually
the least common procedure

29:29.146 --> 29:31.424
I am doing in the PRT.Mm.

29:31.562 --> 29:34.358
I'm mostly providing
wellness checks,

29:34.496 --> 29:39.018
prenatal care, annual...
pelvic exams, pap smears.

29:39.156 --> 29:41.365
Since so many clinics
have closed

29:41.503 --> 29:44.852
in the last several months,
I'm the only option they have.

29:44.990 --> 29:47.199
It's exhausting.

29:52.169 --> 29:53.239
It's a disaster.

29:53.377 --> 29:54.482
Hmm.

29:56.346 --> 29:59.107
And I can't take a break.

29:59.245 --> 30:01.800
If I take a break, I mean,
who-- who's gonna do the work?

30:01.938 --> 30:03.284
