that you take a break,

30:03.422 --> 30:05.320
I thought you were gonna
throw the tablet at him.

30:05.458 --> 30:06.528
Oh, I almost did.

30:08.254 --> 30:09.393
What happened?

30:09.531 --> 30:10.705
