31:01.825 --> 31:03.206
Too many people need you.

31:10.040 --> 31:12.698
No sexual activity
for a week.

31:12.836 --> 31:15.218
We want to give the antibiotics
time to do their job.

31:15.356 --> 31:17.530
You already told me, dear.

31:17.668 --> 31:21.741
And I heard it
when you told Norma and Hal.

31:21.880 --> 31:24.641
Just making sure.
Can't have a sick roomie.

31:24.779 --> 31:26.954
Who else is gonna make me
the world's best French toast

31:27.092 --> 31:28.541
