the night shift?

31:28.679 --> 31:31.234
It's all about
a drop of vanilla.

31:31.372 --> 31:33.684
And I'm sorry that Hal
turned out to be such a jerk.

31:33.822 --> 31:35.894
Me too.
Guys can be pigs.

31:36.032 --> 31:37.309
Gay ones, too.

31:39.207 --> 31:40.450
Women can be...

31:42.279 --> 31:45.489
At first, they tell us
not to have sex at all

31:45.627 --> 31:48.320
and that we're sluts
if we enjoy it.

31:48.458 --> 31:51.150
And then they tell us
if we get pregnant,

31:51.288 --> 31:53.221
we must carry the baby
no matter what.

31:53.359 --> 31:57.329
And once we're mothers,
whether by force or by choice,

31:57.467 --> 31:59.503
they judge us for that, too.

31:59.641 --> 32:03.231
Because there's certainly
no way to be a perfect mother.

32:03.369 --> 32:06.614
So, as women,
we get judged and attacked

32:06.752 --> 32:09.444
for every single decision
we ever make.

32:09.582 --> 32:11.999
You want to know the upside
of this misogyny,

32:12.137 --> 32:13.966
this patriarchy?

32:14.104 --> 32:17.694
Women become invisible
around the age of 60,

32:17.832 --> 32:20.697
and then you can do
whatever the hell you like,

32:20.835 --> 32:25.944
including having a lot of great
sex, because no one cares.

32:26.082 --> 32:30.810
And now, I have an antibiotic
and no regrets.

32:30.949 --> 32:34.573
Except, perhaps, for waiting
so long to live my best life.

32:35.884 --> 32:37.196
See you at home, dear.

32:51.728 --> 32:54.041
Winston, I...

32:56.181 --> 32:57.216
They cherry-picked
my quotes,

32:57.354 --> 33:00.909
