out of context.

33:01.048 --> 33:03.705
But I'm making them change it,
and Teddy will help.

33:03.843 --> 33:05.466
But you said it, so...

33:05.604 --> 33:08.400
I also said that you were one
of the most brilliant surgeons

33:08.538 --> 33:11.161
I have ever worked with,
and that we were equal partners.

33:11.299 --> 33:13.508
We came up with
that procedure together.

33:13.646 --> 33:15.752
I-I didn't
even get a mention.

33:15.890 --> 33:17.236
Just one of
the "assistants."

33:17.374 --> 33:19.169
Journalists always want
to characterize me

33:19.307 --> 33:21.137
as some kind of wunderkind
in a league of my own.

33:21.275 --> 33:23.139
And it's just clickbait.
That's it.

33:23.277 --> 33:24.761
Okay, so it's
the journalist's fault.

33:24.899 --> 33:26.901
Winston, I--Take some responsibility.

33:27.039 --> 33:28.592
For once!

33:31.457 --> 33:34.012
I can't control what other
people write about me.

33:35.392 --> 33:36.773
Alright.

33:36.911 --> 33:39.569
When did we stop giving each
other the benefit of the doubt?

33:43.573 --> 33:46.369
I think it's when you said
