33:46.507 --> 33:49.372
And this article
<i>really</i> drives that home.

33:56.482 --> 33:59.106
I want to fix this.

33:59.244 --> 34:01.453
Tell me what to do
to fix this.

34:01.591 --> 34:04.456
- I want to fix us.
- Maggie, there's no fix.

34:04.594 --> 34:07.459
