There's feelings.

34:07.597 --> 34:10.117
Like, my God,
say you're sorry.

34:10.255 --> 34:13.051
Say you
got some things wrong.

34:13.189 --> 34:14.086
Say you didn't mean
to hurt me.

34:14.224 --> 34:15.950
Say you understand
how I feel.

34:16.088 --> 34:18.953
Say you love me
and mean it.

34:19.091 --> 34:21.059
